                        </a></div></div><ol class="sense_single" htag="ol"><li class="sense" hclass="sense" id="alchemist_sng_2" htag="li"><span class="sensetop" hclass="sensetop" htag="span"><span class="def" htag="span" hclass="def">a comedy play (1610) by <a class="Ref" href="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/ben-jonson" title="Ben Jonson definition"><span class="ndv">Ben Jonson</span></a> about a man who pretends to be an <a class="Ref" href="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/alchemist#alchemist_topg_1" title="alchemist definition"><span class="ndv">alchemist</span></a> <span class="gloss" hclass="gloss" htag="span">(= a person who was thought to be able to turn ordinary metal into gold)</span> in order to cheat people out of their money. Many people consider it to be Jonson's greatest play.</span></span>    <div id="ring-links-box">
